---
// Abschluss-CTA der Kirchortrat-Seite Herz Jesu. Eigene Klassen astro-hjkcta.
---
<section class="astro-hjkcta">
  <div class="astro-hjkcta__in">
    <p class="astro-hjkcta__headline">Fragen oder Anliegen?</p>
    <p class="astro-hjkcta__lead">Der Kirchortrat freut sich &uuml;ber R&uuml;ckmeldungen aus der Gemeinde. Sprechen Sie uns einfach an.</p>
    <a class="astro-hjkcta__btn" href="mailto:azerlik@web.de">Annette Albert-Zerlik schreiben</a>
    <a class="astro-hjkcta__back" href="/kirchorte/herz-jesu/">&#8592; Zur&uuml;ck zu Herz&nbsp;Jesu</a>
    <div class="astro-hjkcta__address">
      <span>Herz Jesu &middot; Mathildestra&szlig;e 30 &middot; 60599 Frankfurt</span>
      <a href="tel:+4969695975850">069 695 97 58 50</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style is:global>
.astro-hjkcta{padding:56px 0;background:#2c2420;width:100vw;position:relative;left:50%;margin-left:-50vw;margin-right:-50vw}
.astro-hjkcta__in{max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 32px;text-align:center;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:14px}
.astro-hjkcta__headline{font-family:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif;font-size:32px;color:#fff;margin:0;line-height:1.2}
.astro-hjkcta__lead{color:rgba(255,255,255,.72);font-size:16px;max-width:520px;margin:0}
.astro-hjkcta__btn{display:inline-block;background:#9a2d2d;color:#fff;padding:13px 28px;border-radius:999px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;transition:background .2s;margin:4px 0}
.astro-hjkcta__btn:hover{background:#c5a55a;color:#1a120e}
.astro-hjkcta__back{color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);font-size:13px;text-decoration:none;transition:color .2s}
.astro-hjkcta__back:hover{color:#c5a55a}
.astro-hjkcta__address{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:4px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);font-size:13px;margin-top:4px}
.astro-hjkcta__address a{color:#c5a55a;text-decoration:none;transition:color .2s}
.astro-hjkcta__address a:hover{color:#fff}
@media(max-width:600px){.astro-hjkcta__in{padding:0 16px}}
</style>
